<subSubSection id="888A4382341265C56EE8AACBB38497E7" pageId="2" pageNumber="81" type="description">
<paragraph id="4227A1764D0125ACB32444F8F8B8503D" pageId="2" pageNumber="81">Measurements.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CA814AC4CB54B24F6482DE93E437C19A" pageId="2" pageNumber="81">Holotype: H 1.84 mm; W 1.05 mm; WB 0.85 mm; AH 0.74, AW 0.56 (holotype). Figs 3-6. Paratype: H 1.82 mm; W 1.08 mm; WB 0.87 mm; AH 0.74, AW 0.56 (holotype). Figs 7-10.</paragraph>
<caption id="FF34477B43879CBAB9460AD5B20B20F4" pageId="2" pageNumber="81">
<paragraph id="111377026A0E6ABA8CD8DB821DBCB2E9" pageId="2" pageNumber="81">
